LDK Solar Lowers Revenue Forecast, Raises Guidance for Margins

-- B y   E h r e n   G o o s s e n s
-- 
2011-04-26T20:40:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/ldk-solar-lowers-revenue-forecast-raises-guidance-for-gross-margins.html
LDK Solar Co., a Chinese solar
company, lowered its forecast for first-quarter revenue and
raised its guidance for gross margins.  LDK said today in a statment that it expects revenue of
$745 million to $755 million, down from its previous guidance of
$800 million to $850 million. Gross margins will range from 30
percent to 31 percent, compared to 27 percent to 29 percent. It
did not give a reason.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ehren Goossens in New York at 
 egoossens1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
